<HEADLINE>
<P>
GIRLS' BASKETBALL ROUNDUP; HOERNER HELPS FULLERTON PULL AWAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Nadia Hoerner scored 19 points and Fullerton pulled away in the fourth quarter 
to beat Apple Valley, 41-35, in the first round of the Brea-Olinda Ladycat 
Classic girls' basketball tournament Tuesday at Brea. 
</P>
<P>
 Cara Dykes scored 10 for Fullerton (3-1), which outscored Apple Valley, 14-8, 
in the fourth quarter. 
</P>
