<TEXT>
<P>
 Point Loma Nazarene entered Tuesday night's nonconference men's basketball 
against Cal Lutheran with a three-game losing streak, but one never would have 
known by the way the Crusaders handled the Kingsmen in a 93-71 victory at San 
Diego. 
</P>
