<P>
 Coach: Kevin Smith (fourth year). 
</P>
<P>
 1993-94: 5-11-6, 3-6-4 in the Sunset League. 
</P>
<P>
 Key returners: Joey Bove, midfielder, Jr.; Steffen Greenly, midfielder, Sr.; 
Scott Hainlen, keeper, Sr; Adam Novak, forward, So.; Craig Ritter, defender, 
Sr.; Joey Vazquez, forward, Jr. 
</P>
<P>
 Key newcomers: Keith Hedenberg, forward, Jr; Ben Martin, forward, So.; Ryan 
