</P>
<P>
 Temperatures (since 1948): 
</P>
<P>
 Highest: 116 degrees on Aug. 24, 1985 in Canoga Park 
</P>
<P>
 Lowest: 20 degrees on Dec. 29, 1954 in Canoga Park 
</P>
