 Auto Thefts by Area: 
</P>
<P>
 (Jan. 1-Nov. 14, 1994) 
</P>
<P>
 Highest: 3,722 in Van Nuys Division Lowest: 2,317 in Devonshire Division * 
</P>
<P>
 Median Ages: 
</P>
<P>
 Highest: 38.7 in Encino-Tarzana 
</P>
<P>
