the in-house design center for Greystone Homes South Coast in Newport Beach. 
Hauck previously was vice president and general manager of the Forecast Group's 
design division in Rancho Cucamonga. She has also worked for M.J. Brock & Sons 
Inc. and Tradewinds-West Inc., both residential developers. 
