<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFCASE: BANKING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by James S. Granelli, Times staff writer 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Refinancing Completed: First American Financial Corp. of Santa Ana, the 
nation's second-largest title insurance company, has refinanced its $65-million 
credit facility and added a $30-million revolving line of credit, all to 
provide more financing at low interest rates. 
</P>
</TEXT>
