<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 High school basketball -- A story in Sunday's editions of The Times 
incorrectly reported that the Santa Paula boys' team had not won a tournament 
in 22 years before winning the Nordhoff tournament on Saturday. Actually, Santa 
Paula had not won the Nordhoff tournament in 22 years but had won other 
tournaments. 
</P>
</TEXT>
